column5: anyone here familiar with deep bay? boat launches etc. you can inbox me any details,thanks.
I can think of 4 places named Deep Bay. I'm guessing you're asking about the one on the road to Killbear?
If you are referring to Deep Bay on Georgian Bay you can launch at Inverlochy Resort it is off of Hwy 559 the road to Kill Bear PP as Chris was saying.

If you are referring to Deep Bay on Georgian Bay you can launch at Inverlochy Resort it is off of Hwy 559 the road to Kill Bear PP as Chris was saying. thats the one. im gonna go out on a limb here and guess that this isnt a free launch? lol have any of you fished here? i might go in about 2 weeks if i can get my boat ready in time,but im told its shallow and rocky.
